Class CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.representation.cisco.nx.CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents the BGP configuration for a single neighbor at the VRF level.

    Configuration commands entered at the CLI config-router-neighbor or config-router-vrf-neighbor levels.
